Find your lyrics anywhere anytime...
Lyric Frenzy is a lyric search application that helps you access over 5 million officially licensed lyrics. You can search lyrics , watch related youtube videos about song , get like & dislike statistics from lastfm and translate to various languages easily if you wonder meaning of song.
- Lyric Frenzy gives you access to top artists and top song lyrics from various countries.
- With Lyric Frenzy you can share your search results with Twitter Share feature (using menu) and let your friends know that you are using Lyric Frenzy.
- Watch related youtube videos about the song easily.
- Learn like dislike statistics from lastfm
